1
00:00:33,210 --> 00:00:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing here?</font>

2
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thirsty and wanted a drink of water.</font>

3
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you c-came all the way out here?</font>

4
00:00:41,170 --> 00:00:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look who's talking.</font>

5
00:00:43,550 --> 00:00:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're out fountain-hopping
 to avoid class, right?</font>

6
00:00:46,530 --> 00:00:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shut up. I-I came here 'cause I'm 
kind of d-doing research on school water.</font>

7
00:00:53,130 --> 00:00:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Research? Oh?</font>

8
00:00:57,360 --> 00:01:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm actually quite particular 
about the water here at school.</font>

9
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then where did you go to 
drink water th-this morning?</font>

10
00:01:06,130 --> 00:01:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heh. If it's early in the day,
like first or second period,</font>

11
00:01:09,290 --> 00:01:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's gotta be west building, second floor,
 next to the classroom.</font>

12
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At that time of day, the water in 
the pipes is still from the day before.</font>

13
00:01:16,370 --> 00:01:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only does it have less of a chlorine taste,
but it's cool in the morning, even in summer.</font>

14
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the finest drinking water.</font>

15
00:01:28,190 --> 00:01:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

16
00:01:29,190 --> 00:01:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's weak.</font>

17
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? How can you say that?</font>

18
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-West building, second floor is b-best 
during lunch break, just before lunch.</font>

19
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lunch break, you say?</font>

20
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's no way the upper floors 
are fit for use after noon.</font>

21
00:01:44,490 --> 00:01:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The chlorine smell gets stronger 
and the water becomes lukewarm.</font>

22
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Amateur.</font>

23
00:01:50,380 --> 00:01:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Warm water is much gentler
 on the s-stomach.</font>

24
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha... B-But the chlorine...</font>

25
00:01:57,680 --> 00:02:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Once your nose adjusts 
to the ch-chlorine smell...</font>

26
00:02:01,910 --> 00:02:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Adjusts"? Wait! You can't mean...</font>

27
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...i-it covers up the smell of the bathroom.</font>

28
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You eat lunch in the bathroom?!</font>

29
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I'd never asked.
Just eat in the club room!</font>

30
00:02:20,810 --> 00:02:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Komari-chan. Nukumizu.</font>

31
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys doing way out here?</font>

32
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. After school, I want you
 both to come to the classroom.</font>

33
00:02:31,770 --> 00:02:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koto has an important announcement.</font>

34
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

35
00:02:35,850 --> 00:02:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, see you later.</font>

36
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0f0f09">Literature Club</font></b></font></font>

37
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahem. I gathered you all 
here today for one reason.</font>

38
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have decided that we shall 
set sail on the open net.</font>

39
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="16"><font color="#1b120a">Absent Today</font></font></b></font></font>

40
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will submit our works to the 
"Become a Literary Icon" site.</font>

41
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are we suddenly doing that?</font>

42
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The student council got on my case
 at the last club presidents' meeting.</font>

43
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They asked why we list composition as an
 activity when we haven't written anything.</font>

44
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? This is the literature club, 
but you haven't written anything?</font>

45
00:04:48,010 --> 00:04:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We say, "Write, write!" 
and then don't write. That is our way.</font>

46
00:04:51,220 --> 00:05:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="14"><font face="Arial Black"><b><font color="#1c2824"><font color="#352e28">Literature Club</font></font></b></font></font></font>

47
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we published a zine, we'd have 
to pay for paper and printing costs,</font>

48
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we have no distribution channels.</font>

49
00:04:56,970 --> 00:05:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes sense. Publishing online 
is much more practical for a club.</font>

50
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So to that end...</font>

51
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This weekend, the literature club
 is holding a training camp!</font>

52
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

53
00:05:07,770 --> 00:05:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was an opening at the youth house 
this weekend. I was able to get two rooms—</font>

54
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on a minute! 
The weekend's only two days away!</font>

55
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speed equals survival in 
today's publishing business.</font>

56
00:05:19,250 --> 00:05:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an7}<b><font size="10"><font color="#706e67">Honestly, I want to hide in my room this weekend</font></font></b></font></font>

57
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't get it, do you?</font>

58
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you still say that 
after hearing this one word?</font>

59
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Canned.</font>

60
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Canned"? As in when an author is
 confined to a hotel room to write?</i></font>

61
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

62
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? What's with that reaction?</i></font>

63
00:05:37,850 --> 00:05:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you always wanted to? 
Doesn't it get you pumped?</font>

64
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Canned is cool!</font>

65
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="25"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#1f1e18">All Deadlines
Are Bad</font></b></font></font></font>

66
00:05:43,850 --> 00:05:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'd like each of you to come up
with a plot by this weekend.</font>

67
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you decided what 
you're going to write, Senpai?</font>

68
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thinking of writing an 
isekai reincarnation story.</font>

69
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, Mishima commits seppuku.
Then he gets reincarnated.</font>

70
00:05:57,710 --> 00:06:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dazai tries to follow by drowning himself in 
the Tamagawa Aqueduct. And that's the intro.</font>

71
00:06:01,990 --> 00:06:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's rated X, so I wouldn't be 
able to show it to you... kids...</font>

72
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rated X?</font>

73
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ungood.</font>

74
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shikiya? How long have you been there?</font>

75
00:06:18,780 --> 00:06:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsukinoki-senpai, 
a training camp requires...</font>

76
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a proposal... submission.</font>

77
00:06:27,610 --> 00:06:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I'll have the 
president bring one tomorrow.</font>

78
00:06:31,770 --> 00:06:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

79
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shikiya from the student council.</font>

80
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The student council is... 
always... watching you.</font>

81
00:06:43,850 --> 00:06:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shikiya, isn't the council 
going a little hard on us?</font>

82
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we go after all the clubs.</font>

83
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Costs. Cuts. Dissolution. Annihilation.</font>

84
00:06:57,850 --> 00:07:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's wrong with this girl? At least blink!</i></font>

85
00:06:57,850 --> 00:07:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Costs. Cuts. Dissolution. Annihilation.</font>

86
