 Introduction</font></b></font></font></font>

89
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="14"><b><font color="#554f4d">Ehima Outdoor Activity Center</font></b></font></font>

90
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A training camp? That sounds like fun.</font>

91
