<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#d4d1ce">{\an7}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></font>

92
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="10"><b><font color="#554f4d">A youth facility jointly operated by the cities of Tahara
 and Toyohashi. Guests can enjoy outdoor activities, sports,
 and camping in a wonderful environment with a panoramic
 view of Mikawa Bay.</font></b></font></font>

93
00:07:06,610 --> 00:07:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know about that. They said we'd
 be "canned." It might not be much fun.</font>

94
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's even a beach nearby.</font>

95
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still have my swimsuit from 
last year. I hope it's okay.</font>

96
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wait a minute. 
Are you planning to come, too?</font>

97
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yesterday, on the way home, 
I ran into Sosuke's mom.</font>

98
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:29,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're childhood friends, 
so our families are friendly, too.</font>

99
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Another heavy story begins.</i></font>

100
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sosuke's mom said, "I haven't seen you in 
the mornings recently. Is everything okay?"</font>

101
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, both families got the wrong idea 
and thought Sosuke and I were fighting,</font>

102
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they're planning to throw a "make-up" 
barbecue this weekend. As a surprise.</font>

103
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please, I'm begging you! 
Take me to the ocean with you!</font>

104
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to go that far. 
You could just go out for a bit instead.</font>

105
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you mocking my father's 
passion for barbecuing?</font>

106
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll keep grilling for hours 
and hours until I get home!</font>

107
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you aren't even in the lit club—</font>

108
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll join! I'll join right this minute!</font>

109
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<b><font size="10"><font color="#425758">This is Yanami Anna</font></font></b></font>

