<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<b><font size="12"><font color="#5a7071">PM</font></font></b></font>

120
00:08:13,010 --> 00:08:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is she gonna be okay? 
Can she even write a novel?</i></font>

121
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then again, it's my first time writing, too.</i></font>

122
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What are we gonna do?</i></font>

123
00:08:29,330 --> 00:08:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nukumizu! Wh-What are you doing here?</font>

124
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are <i>you</i> doing here?</font>

125
00:08:34,490 --> 00:08:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Impolite!</font>

126
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were impolite first.</font>

127
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But whatever. Adding "-san" is a pain, anyway.</font>

128
00:08:41,370 --> 00:08:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you here to check out light novels, too?</font>

129
00:08:41,370 --> 00:08:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an7}<font size="14"><b><font color="#e0ebe8">New Comics</font></b></font></font></font>

130
00:08:44,210 --> 00:08:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't know much about them, 
so I thought I should study some.</font>

131
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't decided what to write, have you?</font>

132
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've actually already started writing.</font>

133
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Really?</font>

134
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-More importantly, is Y-Yanami...</font>

