<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman">{\an1}<font size="10">Good Night at the Late-Late-Night Café</font></font></font>

140
00:08:59,770 --> 00:09:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Yanami joining the lit club, too?</font>

141
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like it. Is that a problem?</font>

142
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yanami's cute. Yakishio's c-cute, too.</font>

143
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you aren't ugly, either, Komari.</font>

144
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

145
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

146
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Pretty girls never join
 the l-literature club.</font>

147
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hold it right there! You need to apologize 
to all lit club girls everywhere!</i></font>

148
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do it! Now!</i></font>

149
00:09:51,410 --> 00:09:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big brother, are you on your way home?</font>

150
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You sure are late today. Shopping?</font>

151
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We're having curry udon today.</font>

152
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big brother, I actually won't be home 
this weekend. Is that all right?</font>

153
00:10:05,070 --> 00:10:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I don't really care.</font>

154
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't get lonely and 
