316
00:17:27,090 --> 00:17:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea you were <i>the</i> Tarosuke-sensei, 
whose stories have amassed over 20,000 points.</font>

317
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you gonna publish it as a book?</font>

318
