327
00:17:38,410 --> 00:17:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="30"><font color="#e03c48">Huge Volume</font></font></font></font>

328
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. Present for you.</font>

329
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where'd you get all this?</font>

330
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemon-chan jumped into the beach 
flag contest and won this as a prize.</font>

331
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You were amazing.</font>

332
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, please continue.</font>

333
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, we should change 
and head back to the lodge.</font>

334
00:17:55,810 --> 00:17:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

335
00:17:57,110 --> 00:18:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Komari-chan, you haven't 
gone in the water yet, have you?</font>

336
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, well...</font>

337
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be right back!</font>

338
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have fun!</font>

339
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go too crazy!</font>

340
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#191d16">Yakisoba</font></font></b></font></font>

341
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koto, does that one look ready?</font>

342
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Food tastes so much better outside!</font>

343
00:18:21,530 --> 00:18:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's still way too soon.</font>

344
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I haven't had b-beef in a while.</font>

345
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure?</font>

346
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How was it, Komari-chan? 
Didn't the water feel great?</font>

347
00:18:25,180 --> 00:18:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but this one's done. Here.</font>

348
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I-It was salty.</font>

349
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

350
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I know, right? It feels so good!</font>

351
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it. They're all the type...</i></font>

352
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to eat it rare without a second thought!</i></font>

353
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I can't just stand here 
waiting for time to run out.</i></font>

354
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to have to eat it raw!</i></font>

355
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu-kun, we just put those on. 
Let's wait for them to cook a bit.</font>

356
00:18:55,670 --> 00:18:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're a real glutton, aren't you?</font>

357
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. If you're hungry, eat this.</font>

358
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you very much.</font>

359
00:19:04,090 --> 00:19:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone at a nearby spot 
just shared these with us.</font>

360
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A middle schooler, maybe?
 She was so cute.</font>

361
00:19:10,490 --> 00:19:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Red rice?</i></font>

362
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Immobulus! Expulso!</font>

363
00:19:23,230 --> 00:19:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll use the last of the coals to raise 
this one right. I'll name her Setsuko.</i></font>

364
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you like fireworks, Yanami-san?</font>

365
00:19:30,610 --> 00:19:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted dessert first.</font>

366
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gonna toast marshmallows?</font>

367
00:19:33,610 --> 00:19:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da! Mixed organ meats!</font>

368
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would ya look at that?</font>

369
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you a-doin'?</font>

370
00:19:41,870 --> 00:19:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

371
00:19:43,470 --> 00:19:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, well, look...</font>

372
00:19:47,910 --> 00:19:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are too big to do alone. 
I'll do them with you.</font>

373
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, come on. I can handle this much myself.</font>

374
00:19:53,370 --> 00:19:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Look at those two. 
I wish they'd hurry up and get married.</i></font>

375
00:19:58,890 --> 00:20:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's pretty.</font>

376
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out, watch out!</font>

377
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, be careful!</font>

378
00:20:01,980 --> 00:20:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there's one left. I'll have that.</font>

379
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Setsuko!</font>

380
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? "Setsuko"?</font>

381
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, uh, I mean...</font>

382
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, if you want it, just say so.</font>

383
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. Aah.</font>

384
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good, right?</font>

385
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

386
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how much is that worth?</font>

387
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, um... 700?</font>

388
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

389
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just teasing.</font>

390
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot! Watch out!</font>

391
00:20:55,730 --> 00:20:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Komari-chan, are you hurt at all?</font>

392
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm okay.</font>

393
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">President, your hand...</font>

394
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me. What would've 
happened if you'd injured your face?</font>

395
00:21:11,830 --> 00:21:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It doesn't really matter 
if my face gets hurt.</font>

396
00:21:14,810 --> 00:21:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be stupid. Of course it matters.</font>

397
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody looks at my face or anything, anyway.</font>

398
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you do, right?</font>

399
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really want to relive a bad memory 
every day when you look in the mirror?</font>

400
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't want that to happen.</font>

401
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-President...</font>

402
00:21:35,150 --> 00:21:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So don't say stuff like that. 
You gotta take care of yourself. Okay?</font>

403
00:21:57,750 --> 00:22:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">President Tamaki...</font>

404
00:22:01,990 --> 00:22:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like you!</font>

405
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

406
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Komari-chan?</font>

407
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-President...</font>

408
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I've always liked you.</font>

409
00:22:17,620 --> 00:22:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You actually pay attention to me.</font>

410
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes me so happy.</font>

411
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like you. So please...</font>

412
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please go out with me!</font>

